  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t上次8月份左右，外媒集体担忧中国经济面临大萧条，我果断买了些黄金基金，小赚了一笔。<br/>\r\n话说国庆暴跌时把我吓一跳，所幸又涨回来了。<br/>\r\n后来想黄金是经济不稳定时期的避险资产，而国庆假期面临一个消费小高潮，这是可预测的稳定收入，所以黄金暴跌。同样的道理也许适用今年春节。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmJjZThkZDZmNDdjNjllM2I2MWM4LnBuZz93aWR0aD00OTImaGVpZ2h0PTQ3Mg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fbce8dd6f47c69e3b61c8.png?width=492&amp;height=472\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fbce8dd6f47c69e3b61c8.png?width=492&amp;height=472\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fbce8dd6f47c69e3b61c8.png?width=492&amp;height=472\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
